  "description": "Stacker is a triple quadrilateral key generator and layer-priority encoder for your modular video synthesizer. Feed Stacker horizontal and vertical waveforms from DWO3, DSG3, Scrolls, or Angles to produce three stacked quadrilateral shapes on the outputs. Learn more about Stacker on our documentation website!"
